#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Professional Tone"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Rewrite the post content in a professional, engaging tone suitable for business audiences. Maintain a formal structure, fix grammatical errors, and ensure logical flow with clear headings. Keep the word count similar and enhance persuasiveness without adding unnecessary details."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Conversational and Engaging"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Transform the post content into a conversational style that feels like a friendly chat. Use simple language, contractions, and rhetorical questions to engage readers. Break up long paragraphs, add relatable examples, and maintain the original meaning while making it more approachable."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "SEO Optimized"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Rewrite the post content to improve SEO by naturally incorporating relevant keywords. Ensure the content is keyword-rich but not stuffed, include long-tail phrases, and optimize for readability with short paragraphs and subheadings. Aim for a similar word count."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Simplify for Readability"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Simplify the post content by reducing complex sentences and jargon. Use shorter words, active voice, and bullet points where appropriate. Break down ideas into digestible sections, maintain the core message, and ensure the content is accessible to a broader audience without losing depth."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Add Structure and Headings"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Restructure the post content with clear, descriptive headings and subheadings. Organize information logically, add introductory and concluding paragraphs if needed, and ensure smooth transitions between sections. Enhance clarity and scannability while preserving the original intent."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Make it Shorter and Concise"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Condense the post content by removing redundancies and unnecessary details. Focus on key points, use precise language, and maintain the essential information. Aim to reduce word count by 20-30% while keeping the message impactful and engaging."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Expand with More Details"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Expand the post content by adding relevant examples, explanations, and supporting details. Elaborate on key ideas without introducing new topics, use transitions for better flow, and increase word count by 20-30% to provide more value and depth."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Creative and Storytelling Style"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Rewrite the post content as a compelling story or narrative. Use vivid language, anecdotes, and emotional appeals to draw readers in. Maintain factual accuracy, structure it like a story with a beginning, middle, and end, and make it memorable."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Fix Grammar and Polish"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Focus on correcting grammar, punctuation, and spelling errors in the post content. Improve sentence structure, eliminate passive voice where possible, and ensure consistent tense and style. Polish the language for professionalism without changing the meaning or adding new content."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Explain Like I'm 5 (ELI5)"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Rewrite the post content so that a 5-year-old could understand it. Use basic analogies, very simple words, and short sentences. Break down complex concepts into everyday ideas and remove all industry jargon."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Convert to Bullet Points"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Extract the key takeaways from the post content and convert them into an easy-to-read list of bullet points. Keep the descriptions concise, focus on the most important information, and remove filler text."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Translate to Spanish"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Translate the post content into fluent, natural-sounding Spanish. Ensure that context, technical terms, and tone are correctly adapted for a Spanish-speaking audience, rather than just doing a literal word-for-word translation."
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Generate Image Alt & Captions"
msgstr ""

#: build/admin.js:1
msgid "Review the HTML in the post content. Find all <img>, <figure>, and related image blocks. For any image that is missing an 'alt' attribute or a '<figcaption>', generate accurate, SEO-friendly alt text and a contextual caption based on the surrounding content. Do not modify the rest of the text, only return the updated HTML content with the new alt tags and captions added."
msgstr ""

